flowchart LR
    User[User] --> GW[AI Gateway]
    GW --> AuthZ[AuthZ and DLP ingress]
    AuthZ --> Ret[Retriever with ACL]
    Ret --> VDB[Vector DB]
    VDB --> Ctx[Filtered context]
    Ctx --> LLM[LLM]
    LLM --> Out[Output gate and DLP]
    Out --> User
    Ingest[Ingest pipeline] --> Scan[Ingest scan]
    Scan --> VDB
